    <refsection id="Description_MMR_IdealGearR2T0">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>This block is an ideal gearbox transforming rotational into translational motion (rack and pignon system), with:</para>
        <para>
            <latex>
                \begin{eqnarray}
                ratio = \frac{\Large{\omega_{in}}}{\Large{V_{out}}}
                \end{eqnarray}
            </latex>
        </para>
        <para>
            where <latex>\omega_{in}\:</latex> (resp. <latex>V_{out}\:</latex>) is the angular velocity of the pignon (resp. rack) in
            rad/s (resp. m/s).
        </para>
    </refsection>
